lls, changing trigger logic, attacking targets, and additional effects or characteristics. You can concentrate your passive skills on an active skill to get an ultimate skill that destroys the sky. You can strengthen your basic attributes to be a veritable muscular man, and you can also strengthen your aura skills to become a pendant tool. How many genres of heroes can be constructed from diversified skill combinations waiting for you to explore.<h2 class="bb_tag">Extremely rich level gameplay</h2>As a leader, how do you allocate the brave to different levels of adventure? <br><br>1.	Expedition forest-forest need hard power, develop hang up is the key. <br>2.	Expedition hang up-grope for the highest production efficiency team configuration, don''t forget to take to open the treasure chest the tools. <br>3.	Training ground- rapidly promote a good place for awakening metempsychosis hero hero level.  <br>4.	Mines-equip your heroes with miners‚Äô work permits and send them to mines. Treasures such as golden pickaxe and miner''s hat can double the efficiency of your hero. <br>5.	Jungle-Heroes equipped with an adventure certificate can enter the jungle treasure hunt. Of course not all heroes have the qualifications to obtain an adventure certificate. <br>6.	 Double Secret Realm-Double Secret Realm that only men or women are allowed to enter. Do you want to go with your best all-girl cast?<h2 class="bb_tag">Characteristic town work</h2>Not only can you send heroes out on expeditions and adventures, but you can also arrange jobs for them in towns. Arranging heroes into buildings can provide different bonuses to buildings. There are castles, taverns, equipment shops, blacksmith shops, merchants, training grounds and other buildings in the town. The rich town management can help you improve your team.', 8.19, 'EUR', 'https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steam/apps/1335240/header.jpg?t=1628504849', CURRENT_DATE(), 'GAME', NULL);
INSERT INTO Article (id, title, description, price, currency, picture_url, release_date, article_type, id_base_article) VALUES (1335300, 'The Warlin of Heroes', '<img src="https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steam/apps/1335300/extras/INc1_en.png?t=1640421299" /><br><br>‚ÄúThe Warlin of Heroes‚Äù is a martial arts card game with rogue-like elements. As players climb the tower to level up, they will collect martial arts techniques that can be used to form unique and flashy card combos. Will you use the mighty Descending Dragon Palm into an elegant Leap of 1000 Li? Or will you use the unrivaled Solitary Sword with supreme Taiji Boxing? The choice is in your hands.<br> <br>Characteristics<br>The game contains an in-depth and extensive martial arts system with 48 external techniques, 20 internal techniques, and 19 Qigong techniques. In total, there are 87 martial arts techniques with their own unique effects and skills. Each technique can be combined for all new exciting gameplay!<br><br>Gameplay<br>The game is a classic tower climbing game with each level presenting a random variety of choices to the player, such as: combat, events, shops, meditation, recovery, and rewards. Choose wisely to increase your strength and take on challenges accordingly to clear levels and beat the bosses.<br><br>Combat<br>The game‚Äôs combat is based on the strengths and weaknesses of the five elements in a guessing game against your opponent. Each element is strong against two elements, but weak to two as well. Combine the special effects of skills with your ultimate in intense simulated martial arts combat.<br><br>Story<br>The story takes place in a martial arts world with four new schools established by the masters Liang, Jin, Gu, and Wen. The heroes of Warlin will retell their tales in an all new adventure!<br><br><img src="https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steam/apps/1335300/extras/INc2_en.png?t=1640421299" /><br>Here is our plan for the following updates. Any changes or immediate bug fixes will be specified in the current update log.<br> <br>Version[B1.1.0.ST]<br>1. Update character voices and non-combat related sound effects, such as: in-combat button presses, leveling up, opening chests, etc.<br>2. Fix Settings content and add a volume bar.<br>3. Add a notification at the beginning of combat.<br>4. Fix the skip button for the tutorial.<br>5. Fix the English translation for the tutorial.<br><br>Version[B1.1.1.ST]<br>1.	Opened up the Steam achievement system.<br>2.	Updated English voice acting for the enemies.<br>3.	Updated English translation for events.<br>4.	Changed calculation of gaining/losing money from events.<br>5Ôºé	Updated fight rewards to events and added a cancelation feature.<br>6.	Updated character save data.<br><br><br>Version[B1.1.2.ST]<br>1.Optimize the tower climbing mode and update boss combat.<br>2.Optimize the Chinese and English explanations for techniques.<br><br>Version[B1.1.3.ST]<br>1.Update combat, reprogram combat calculation, optimize combat rules, and fix combat bugs.<br>2.Add combat sound effects.<br>3.Improve the tutorial and add help notifications.<br><br>[h]Version[B2.0.4.ST]<br>1.Update battle animations to better differentiate between different attacks. <br>2.Add 4 new characters.<br>[/h]<br><br><br>Version[B2.1.0.ST]<br>1.Improve Adventure Mode to become a martial arts RPG.<br>2.Add 50 new martial arts techniques.<br><br>Version[B2.2.0.ST]<br>1.  Improve Versus Mode.', 5.69, 'EUR', 'https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steam/apps/1335300/header.jpg?t=1640421299', CURRENT_DATE(), 'GAME', NULL);
INSERT INTO Article (id, title, description, price, currency, picture_url, release_date, article_type, id_base_article) VALUES (1335360, 'Chef Chen', '„ÄäChef Chen„Äã is a cooperative multiplayer game, where you can cook the monsters in the fantasy world with many adventures and enjoy the food together. Currently the game supports up to 4 players (Local) and Steam Remote Play. Let‚Äôs work together and make delicious dishes! <br><br>Chef Chen came to the fantasy world by chance. He encounters a group of hungry animals, and sees monster bodies everywhere.  With Chef Chen''s excellent cooking skill, he turns the monsters into delicious dishes! That saves his animal friends who were almost starved to death and it replenishes their strength and magic power so that they can continue the journey of adventure.<br><br>Would you like to sit down with your friends and have a nice meal? Play the role of Chef Chen and use your talent and team up with your friends to defeat the monsters. Let''s cook a good meal together, and then enjoy the gourmet.<h2 class="bb_tag">*  Food to hunt</h2><img src="https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steam/apps/1335360/extras/steam_gif_1.gif?t=1643377253" /><h2 class="bb_tag">*  Food to hunt</h2><img src="https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steam/apps/1335360/extras/steam_gif_2.gif?t=1643377253" /><h2 class="bb_tag">*  Limited kitchen knife availability</h2><img src="https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steam/apps/1335360/extras/steam_gif_3.gif?t=1643377253" />', 8.19, 'EUR', 'https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steam/apps/1335360/header.jpg?t=1643377253', CURRENT_DATE(), 'GAME', NULL);
INSERT INTO Article (id, title, description, price, currency, picture_url, release_date, article_type, id_base_article) VALUES (1335370, 'DVR Simulator', 'DVR Simulator is a Drone Racing FPV Simulator. Are you already an FPV pilot? Start your training now with the Freestyle and Racing modes.<h2 class="bb_tag">Features</h2><ul class="bb_ul"><li> Freestyle Mode<br></li><li> Racing Mode<br></li><li> Physics Editor<br></li><li> Virtual Reality</li></ul><h2 class="bb_tag">Physics Editor</h2>The in-game physics editor allows you to change a lot of parameters such as drag, gravity, motor power, etc.<br><ul class="bb_ul"><li> Drag, Angular Drag, Interpolation times, Gravity<br></li><li> Rates and Throttle mid/expo<br></li><li> 3D settings<br></li><li> More</li></ul><h2 class="bb_tag">Virtual Reality</h2>Do you have a VR headset? Use it to simulate FPV goggles! Real FPV goggles use the same image for both eyes resulting in no motion sickness. <br>This is the default behavior when VR is enabled, it''s like watching a big movie screen, there is no motion sickness.<br>Of course, you can enable the stereo mode and experiment with a new level of FPV immersion. This mode is not comfortable and is subject to motion sickness.<h2 class="bb_tag">Inputs</h2>The simulator works with both gamepads and real radio transmitters. A calibration process helps you to configure your radio transmitter.<br>Calibrations are stored in a file that can be shared with friends that have the same radio transmitter.', 8.19, 'EUR', 'https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steam/apps/1335370/header.jpg?t=1640158450', CURRENT_DATE(), 'GAME', NULL);
INSERT INTO Article (id, title, description, price, currency, picture_url, release_date, article_type, id_base_article) VALUES (1335400, 'Rangers', 'This is a zombie survival game for one player and for cooperation in 4 players.<br><br><strong>The game now includes:</strong><br>Single player with co-op for 4players - <strong>Host / Join</strong> sessions - <strong>hosted game</strong>, player characters, chat system, dynamic crosshairs, points system, random weapon box, spectating &amp; respawn system, Power-Up drops, revive system, deadly things like a train...<br><br>This game is also support project for my new &quot;VR&quot; game.', 4.99, 'EUR', 'https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steam/apps/1335400/header.jpg?t=1604855392', CURRENT_DATE(), 'GAME', NULL);
INSERT INTO Article (id, title, description, price, currency, picture_url, release_date, article_type, id_base_article) VALUES (1335440, 'Tyrgard Archer VR', '<img src="https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steam/apps/1335440/extras/Featuresimg.png?t=1599555662" /><h2 class="bb_tag">- Challenging bow play -</h2> Easy to learn, extremely rewarding to master.<h2 class="bb_tag">- A variety of enemies -</h2>Do your best to hold back the tide of mythical creatures, all posing different challenges to overcome.<br><br><img src="https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steam/apps/1335440/extras/closeonegif.gif?t=1599555662" /><h2 class="bb_tag">- Control the pace of the battle -</h2>Need more of a challenge? Start the waves early for a high risk high reward play.<h2 class="bb_tag">- Beautiful scenery -</h2>Breath in the fresh air of the nordic valley, the calming sounds of the ocean and the seaguls. Enjoy the silence before the storm.<h2 class="bb_tag">- Customize your playthrough -</h2>Choose between powerful abilities as you progress, increasing your own lethality, but also that of your enemy.<br><br><img src="https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steam/apps/1335440/extras/explodingdragongif.gif?t=1599555662" /><br><br>Set in the idyllic viking village of Tyrgard, you are set to protect your people from an onslaught of vicious mythical creatures.<br><br>As a master archer, you unlock an array of unique skills and abilities, while advancing through waves of enemies.<br>But just as you, they too become more powerful as the battle progresses.<br><br>Get familiar with your bow and abilities to learn how to best prioritize threats.<br>The difficulty increases as you progress and you will encounter new types of enemies, who will challenge your mastery, reflex and awareness.<br>- You will not survive, so make it count.', 1.59, 'EUR', 'https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steam/apps/1335440/header.jpg?t=1599555662', CURRENT_DATE(), 'GAME', NULL);
INSERT INTO Article (id, title, description, price, currency, picture_url, release_date, article_type, id_base_article) VALUES (1335500, 'Hell''s High Harmonizers', '<strong>Hell is lively today!<br>A loose life simulation of living in Hell.</strong><br><br>Hell, it''s a place where the dead live.<br>The inhabitants are always busy with reckoning, remorse, slacking off, and rebellion.<br>You are the Harmonizer, an official of Hell. You will work for the peace of your newly assigned ward 69371.<br><br>Sometimes we''ll consult with the residents, sometimes we''ll cooperate with them, and sometimes we''ll enjoy life in Hell!<br><br><strong>Character Create</strong><br>People, inorganics, and everything else! Freedom and unique character create.<br><img src="https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steam/apps/1335500/extras/store001.png?t=1637636757" /><br><br><strong>Various Unique Residents</strong><br>People, lizards, bones, and machines? The residents of Hell, who are diverse in appearance and birth.<br><img src="https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steam/apps/1335500/extras/store002.png?t=1637636757" /><br><br><strong>Exploration</strong><br>Explore Hell with the residents! <br>Traps, enemies, and wonderful treasures await you!', 3.99, 'EUR', 'https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steam/apps/1335500/header.jpg?t=1637636757', CURRENT_DATE(), 'GAME', NULL);
